      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"honoring the struggle\" part feels so forced. like, why bother patching up a sinking ship? if the end result is just absolute nothingness, then every bit of effort we put into staying alive, or working, or loving, or even just breathing, is just delaying the inevitable and adding unnecessary weight to a life that doesn't actually mean anything in the long run. it feels more like we're just prolonging a farce.",
